== PSGML-Utils ==

[https://hg.sr.ht/~nolda/psgml-utils PSGML-Utils] by Andreas Nolda is a set of extensions for PsgmlMode. They consist of the following files:

* [https://hg.sr.ht/~nolda/psgml-utils/browse/psgml-superedit.el psgml-superedit.el]:
  additional editing functions for use with PSGML
* [https://hg.sr.ht/~nolda/psgml-utils/browse/psgml-run.el psgml-run.el]:
  functions for running validation and transformation scenarios in PSGML
* [https://hg.sr.ht/~nolda/psgml-utils/browse/psgml-xml.el psgml-xml.el]:
  an XML mode derived from PSGML's SGML mode
